data.description: Hagan-Burke Trail allows for a convenient 10-min walk to downtown Carmel. Primary bedroom on main lvl that offers extra space for sitting room or home office. 3 more full ensuites on both the upper lvl & in the basement in addition to 2 more bedrooms sharing a bathroom, making it perfect for accommodating large or extended families. The property also boasts other desirable features such as a private office, a well-equipped chef's kitchen w/ built-in Viking double oven, gas cooktop & tray ceiling. The basement is spacious and features a double-sided fireplace, daylight windows & full kitchenette, making it ideal for hosting live-in guests. The fully fenced and tree-lined lot provides privacy & serene setting. Hard to find 4 car garage.
